            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Dis Manibus <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Annius Severus vet<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>ranus</abbr></expan> ex <expan><abbr>clas</abbr><ex>se</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetoria</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Mis</abbr><ex>enensi</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>militavit annos XXVI vixit annos XXXXVIII curavit <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Scenti</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Celer
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>pr(aetoria) vermutlich aufgrund eines Fehlers des Steinmetzen erst nachträglich in den Rahmen oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes auf Höhe des Spatiums zwischen clas(se) und Mis(enensi) eingemeißtelt.</p>
            </div>
